      <title>随着房地产市场的下滑，股市上涨提振了加拿大家庭的净资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/stock-rally-buoys-canada-households-net-worth-as-housing-drags</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年年底，全球债券和股票的上涨支撑了加拿大人的财富，抵消了房地产价值的持续下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/stock-rally-buoys-canada-households-net-worth-as-housing-drags</guid>
