    <item>
      <title>日本企业今年计划加薪多少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/here-s-how-much-japanese-firms-plan-to-hike-salaries-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[年度工资谈判的初步结果表明，许多日本工人将获得数十年来最大的涨幅，这对日本央行来说是一个积极的进展，就在几天前，日本央行将召开会议，决定是否结束世界上最后一个负利率制度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/here-s-how-much-japanese-firms-plan-to-hike-salaries-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
